{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01WgmRgXu1GrWHSJkMa2vsMX","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The key issue is clear from the describe output:\n\n```\nCommand:\n  /bin/bash\n  -c\n  if [ \"$POD_NAME\" = \"crdb-cluster-1\" ]; then\n    HTTP_ADDR=\"127.0.0.1:8080\";\n  else\n    HTTP_ADDR=\"0.0.0.0:8080\";\n  fi; exec /cockroach/cockroach start ...\n```\n\nThe `crdb-cluster-1` pod is intentionally binding its HTTP address to `127.0.0.1:8080` (loopback) instead of `0.0.0.0:8080`. This means the readiness/liveness probes from Kubernetes (which come from outside the pod's loopback interface) can't connect to port 8080 - that's why the readiness probe fails with \"connection refused\".\nThe readiness probe is failing because it's trying to reach `10.244.0.117:8080` but getting connection refused, which confirms the HTTP server isn't listening on the pod's actual IP. I need to modify the StatefulSet to remove the special case that restricts `crdb-cluster-1` to loopback binding, so all pods bind to `0.0.0.0:8080` instead.","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":5742,"cache_read_input_tokens":30091,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":5742},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8015f21e-1368-44bb-afee-00dd3cb21624","uuid":"e59f347c-9d39-4b7b-86da-38762a1a3066","request_id":"req_011CbyFdDBKFfbU8LcXH8wpY"}
{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-4-6","id":"msg_01WgmRgXu1GrWHSJkMa2vsMX","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The root cause is clear: `crdb-cluster-1` is intentionally binding its HTTP server to `127.0.0.1:8080` (loopback only), so the Kubernetes health probes coming from the pod's IP can't connect. Let me look at the StatefulSet to fix it."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":5742,"cache_read_input_tokens":30091,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":5742},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"8015f21e-1368-44bb-afee-00dd3cb21624","uuid":"6c2e986f-46b1-4d66-877a-320dff2b2671","request_id":"req_011CbyFdDBKFfbU8LcXH8wpY"}
